{"about_the_game":"<strong>-When you're facing a corruption, will you stop it or ignore it?-</strong><br><br>A 2017 Thailand's phenomenal anti-corruption mobile visual novel is now available on Steam for FREE! Face the real world-inspired corruption cases and experience the consequences by yourself. Developed and produced by Opendream and Khon Thai Foundation.<br><br>In the near future, at the time when corruption is a new normal, Laia exploited the society and became a leader of the world's government. Amita has to travel through time to the past to stop the cause of new normal with a hope to stop corruptions to save her fragile and collapsing future.<br><br>The player will face with the real world-inspired corruption cases in Thailand and required to investigate and collect evidence to <strong>&quot;stop or ignore&quot;</strong> multiple corruption events. Every decisions will affect the story line and future events in the game.<br><br>Corrupt won a silver medal from ASEAN ICT Awards 2017 and multiple local awards for anti-corruption efforts.<br><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> HD graphics<br></li><li> A social gaming that allow players to learn other players' decisions<br></li><li> A consequence system]</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Justice Break!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/927850/988f6c754f94a6b3c9b41026fa605e99d4fbc6ce.jpg"},{"name":"The Time Traveler","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/927850/cba56f082bd6f8afa9cf709d22415c15846ce1fc.jpg"},{"name":"A Sad Couple ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/927850/42eda309ff0724b1b786cab28b42eeeb0b2a3aea.jpg"},{"name":"The Righteous Academy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/927850/c5ccc1e47ac088fb016b959db7d58acc8f1bf349.jpg"},{"name":"A Mysterous Medicine","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamsta